properties.description:
Author: Jilly Webster
Date: 21/06/2023
Description: ASCD-20271 - this pipeline loads data from Ms Dynamics (SQL Server) Asc_deathclaim table to STAGE_CDI (Oracle) CRM_PLAT_DYN_DEATHCLAIM_STG table.

Name - Nikita Varnwal
Date - June 2023
Project - CRM Migration, implemented under CHG######
Description - This pipeline will pull all the data from the required fields from Asc_Deathclaim table from CRM and load it into CRM_PLAT_DYN_DEATHCLAIM_STG table in STAGE_CDI.

activities.name: cd-CRM_PLAT_DYN_DEATHCLAIM_STG
activities.description: pulls data from MS Dynamic table Asc_Deathclaim and copies to the STAGE_CDI table CRM_PLAT_DYN_DEATHCLAIM_STG using SQL query

Name - Nikita Varnwal
Date - June 2023
Project - CRM Migration, implemented copy all the selected field's data of Asc_DeathClaim table from CRM database to  CRM_PLAT_DYN_DEATHCLAIM_STG table of STAGE_CDI database.
